<i>Posted by Taewedar on 09-13-2001 10:11 PM:</i>

<p><b> </b></p>

<p>I'd say you have different tiers of guilds. The highend uber guild raiding TOV and such in general has their epics. They are the ones who want you to have the right faction, all resist gear, etc etc before joining. 2nd tier guilds are the ones stil working on getting members epics, doing the arena in kael for armor and practice, etc etc.<br />
In general most epic's don't take more then three groups at anyone time. So really with a large group of friends of the right class, epics can be done with enough patience.<FONT face="arial, helvetica" size="2"><br>
